  "details": "A vulnerability has been found in c-rick jimeng-mcp 1.10.0. Affected by this vulnerability is the function getFileContent/uploadCoverFile/generateImage/generateVideo of the file src/api.ts. The manipulation of the argument filePath leads to path traversal. The attack may be initiated remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used. The project was informed of the problem early through an issue report but has not responded yet.",
